    NULL,
};
static const struct attribute_group tb_egpu_recover_attr_group = {
    .attrs = tb_egpu_recover_attrs,
};
```
Individual attrs declared via DEVICE_ATTR at nv-tb-egpu-recover.c:766-775 (modes 0444 for read-only counters, 0200 for write-only force_trigger).

